Automata.name: Passenger Land-Transportation System
Automata.comment: Adapted from 'Supervising Passenger Land-Transportation Systems' by K.T. Seow and M. Pasquier. The system is controllable and nonblocking. P-size: 559872 states, Sp-size: 9720000 states, P||Sp-size: 4907968 states. This is an import of a (parametrised) Waters-model.
